      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np, pandas as pd\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "from scipy.optimize import curve_fit\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Eğer monod_df yoksa df'den üret (df de yoksa veri yarat) ---\n",
        "try:\n",
        "    monod_df\n",
        "except NameError:\n",
        "    try:\n",
        "        df\n",
        "    except NameError:\n",
        "        data = \"\"\"Time_h,Biomass_gL,Glucose_gL\n",
        "0,0.2,50\n",
        "2,0.6,44\n",
        "4,1.5,38\n",
        "6,2.7,31\n",
        "8,3.8,24\n",
        "10,4.5,18\n",
        "12,4.8,13\n",
        "14,4.9,9\n",
        "16,5.0,6\n",
        "18,5.0,4\n",
        "\"\"\"\n",
        "        with open(\"fermentation_data.csv\", \"w\") as f: f.write(data)\n",
        "        df = pd.read_csv(\"fermentation_data.csv\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    # monod_df’yi oluştur\n",
        "    eps = 1e-9\n",
        "    lnX = np.log(np.clip(df[\"Biomass_gL\"].values, eps, None))\n",
        "    t   = df[\"Time_h\"].values\n",
        "    mu_est = np.diff(lnX) / np.diff(t)\n",
        "    S = df[\"Glucose_gL\"].values\n",
        "    S_mid = 0.5*(S[1:] + S[:-1])\n",
        "    monod_df = pd.DataFrame({\"S_mid\": S_mid, \"mu_est\": mu_est}).dropna().reset_index(drop=True)\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Monod fonksiyonu ---\n",
        "def monod(S, mu_max, K_S):\n",
        "    return mu_max * S / (K_S + S)\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Veri dizileri ---\n",
        "S_data = monod_df[\"S_mid\"].values\n",
        "mu_data = monod_df[\"mu_est\"].values\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Sınırlı (bounded) fit ---\n",
        "bounds = ([0, 0], [2.0, 100])      # mu_max 0–2 1/h, K_S 0–100 g/L\n",
        "p0 = [0.6, 5.0]\n",
        "\n",
        "popt, pcov = curve_fit(monod, S_data, mu_data, p0=p0, bounds=bounds, maxfev=10000)\n",
        "mu_max_hat, K_S_hat = popt\n",
        "mu_max_se, K_S_se = np.sqrt(np.diag(pcov))\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"mu_max ≈ {mu_max_hat:.3f} ± {mu_max_se:.3f} 1/h\")\n",
        "print(f\"K_S    ≈ {K_S_hat:.3f} ± {K_S_se:.3f} g/L\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Uyum kalitesi ---\n",
        "mu_pred = monod(S_data, mu_max_hat, K_S_hat)\n",
        "ss_res = np.sum((mu_data - mu_pred)**2)\n",
        "ss_tot = np.sum((mu_data - mu_data.mean())**2)\n",
        "R2_nl = 1 - ss_res/ss_tot\n",
        "print(f\"Nonlinear fit R² ≈ {R2_nl:.3f}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Grafikler ---\n",
        "S_line = np.linspace(S_data.min(), S_data.max(), 200)\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(7,5))\n",
        "plt.scatter(S_data, mu_data, label=\"Data (S_mid vs μ_est)\")\n",
        "plt.plot(S_line, monod(S_line, mu_max_hat, K_S_hat),\n",
        "         label=f\"Monod fit\\nμmax={mu_max_hat:.2f}, KS={K_S_hat:.2f}\")\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"Substrate, S (g/L)\"); plt.ylabel(\"Specific growth rate, μ (1/h)\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"Monod Model Fit\"); plt.legend(); plt.grid(True); plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "residuals = mu_data - mu_pred\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(7,4))\n",
        "plt.scatter(mu_pred, residuals)\n",
        "plt.axhline(0, linestyle='--', linewidth=1)\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"Predicted μ\"); plt.ylabel(\"Residuals\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"Residual Plot (Monod Fit)\"); plt.grid(True); plt.show()"
      ],
